&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Health-E Commerce:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Navigating the complexities of consumer-directed health plans is essential, and Health-E Commerce simplifies this process by providing guaranteed eligible products and services through HSA Store® and FSA Store. Our platforms combine eligible product marketplaces, education, exceptional customer service, and integrated technology tools within employee benefit portals.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Through our direct-to-consumer platforms and a network of third-party administrators that partner with employers and employees, we engage customers throughout their entire benefits journey and help them maximize the value of their healthcare dollars.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Health-E Commerce is seeking a Marketing Manager to support the execution of B2B2C and B2B marketing campaigns with a primary focus on HSA Store®. This role will be responsible for building and executing marketing campaigns that reach consumers through our partner ecosystem while also contributing to broader partner marketing initiatives across the business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This includes developing and executing HSA Store campaigns across B2B2C and partner channels; spanning campaign messaging, email marketing, partner-facing assets, and supporting materials that drive consumer engagement and conversion. &amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is ideal for someone who enjoys building campaigns, collaborating with cross-functional teams, and executing marketing initiatives that deliver measurable results.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
