&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Health-E Commerce is seeking a strategic, results-oriented Sr. Ecommerce Manager to lead our ecommerce and personalization efforts. This role owns the development and execution of our site strategy for FSAstore and HSAStore to drive revenue growth through improved site metrics. This is a player-coach role that requires both strategic leadership and hands-on execution. The Sr. Manager will partner closely with creative, UX, data, and product teams to improve our customer journey improve our customer acquisition, engagement, and lifetime value.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
