&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Own and drive the ecommerce strategy for FSAstore and HSAstore, with a clear focus on improving CVR, AOV, and overall revenue.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop and execute seasonal and evergreen site strategies, optimizing onsite merchandising, category prioritization, sorting rule, boosting/burring, informed by consumer insights and performance data.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Lead approval for monthly site flips and content strategy, partnering closely with Marketing on promotional calendars.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
