&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Partner with Data Science and Product to deploy ML-driven recommendation models based on user segmentation and purchase behavior.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
